---
source: crates/henosis-cli/src/lib.rs
expression: command_help()
---
Develop and deploy Henosis component graphs.

Henosis keeps the selected graph and core target in .henosis/context. Graph creation is always explicit.

Usage: henosis <COMMAND>

Commands:
  dev     Continuously typecheck, bundle, deploy, and follow graph status
  deploy  Typecheck, bundle, deploy once, and wait for a terminal graph status
  status  Print the selected graph's current status
  retire  Retire the selected graph
  debug   Low-level packaging and troubleshooting commands
  help    Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
